import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import { Link, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { useAuth } from "../context/AuthContext"; import { db, get, ref } from "../fireba/firebase"; import "./framework.css"; import "./master.css"; import "./style1.css"; import "./dashbord.css"; import profile from "./avatar.png"; import welcome from "./welcome.png"; import photo from "./profile-user.png"; import change from "./cigarette.png"; import setting from "./settings.png"; import friend from "./friends.png"; import multipe from "./multiple-users-silhouette.png"; export default function Dashboard() { const [error, setError] = useState(""); const { currentUser, logout } = useAuth(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const userId = currentUser?.uid; const [name, setName] = useState(""); const [country, setCountry] = useState(""); const [age, setAge] = useState(""); useEffect(() => { const fetchData = async () => { if (!currentUser) { navigate("/login"); return; } setLoading(true); const userId = currentUser.uid; try { const nameSnapshot = await get(ref(db, `users/${userId}/name`)); setName(nameSnapshot.exists() ? nameSnapshot.val() : "N/A"); const countrySnapshot = await get(ref(db, `users/${userId}/country`)); setCountry(countrySnapshot.exists() ? countrySnapshot.val() : "N/A"); const ageSnapshot = await get(ref(db, `users/${userId}/age`)); setAge(ageSnapshot.exists() ? ageSnapshot.val() : "N/A"); } catch (err) { setError("Failed to fetch user data"); } finally { setLoading(false); } }; fetchData(); }, [currentUser, navigate]); async function handleLogout() { setError(""); try { await logout(); navigate("/login"); } catch { setError("Failed to log out"); } } return (
